This paper deals with optimization problems in computer vision and machine learning, which are typically addressed in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also discusses numerical methods and convergence analysis, which are relevant to the sub-categories of cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.CV, and cs.NA, followed by cs.DC and cs.SY.
